org.unisens

Interface EventEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotationEntry, java.lang.Cloneable, Entry, TimedEntry

    public interface EventEntry
extends AnnotationEntry
    EventEntry represents an Entry containing a list of Events. Events have no signal or value data. Each Event has a timstamp and a type and can have a comment. Type and comment are strings.
